            EXAMPLE 
            The file symbols/archsites.s will draw a small square, shown
            as symbol 14 on the -sr font, at each site location.  The
            symbols will be plotted with the pen in position 1, .2 cm
            high.
            
                 mdef=map.def
                 name=archsites
                 sym=23
                 pen=1
                 size=.2
                 font=sr
            
            NOTE 
            If only one map element will be drawn on the map
            composition, the default selection for the file name is
            recommended for use.
            
            The delete key will abort the make.symbol command.
            
